                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Documentation on United States policy with respect to procurement of uranium from
                    the Belgian Congo and cooperation with Belgium in the field of atomic energy is
                    included in volume I in the compilation on foreign policy aspects of United
                    States development of atomic energy.</p>
